146
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:13,759
Come on!

147
00:07:13,759 --> 00:07:14,839
Soccer's the best!

148
00:07:14,879 --> 00:07:15,879
I want to play soccer!

149
00:07:15,879 --> 00:07:16,199
My shoes!

150
00:07:16,279 --> 00:07:16,800
My shoes!

151
00:07:16,879 --> 00:07:17,360
Give them back!

152
00:07:18,079 --> 00:07:19,879
My shoes! Give them back!

153
00:07:20,079 --> 00:07:21,680
I bought those! Give them back!

154
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:22,720
- My shoes! - Let's go!

155
00:07:23,279 --> 00:07:24,079
