162
00:07:35,959 --> 00:07:36,680
Let me score one.

163
00:07:37,839 --> 00:07:38,360
Me too!

164
00:07:38,519 --> 00:07:39,519
Get lost, you guys.

165
00:07:40,439 --> 00:07:41,600
