166
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,199
Happy birthday.

167
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:15,399
Happy birthday.

168
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:16,319
Come on.

169
00:08:19,439 --> 00:08:20,480
Here's to those dreams

170
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:22,959
that were once thrown into the trash can,

171
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:24,480
