176
00:09:15,799 --> 00:09:16,879
Wow, so intense!

177
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:26,960
Changzhou!

178
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:28,840
Let's go!

179
00:09:30,039 --> 00:09:30,879
Changzhou!

180
00:09:31,039 --> 00:09:31,960
Son! Son!

181
00:09:32,159 --> 00:09:32,840
Go for it!

182
00:09:33,799 --> 00:09:34,240
Son!

183
00:09:34,279 --> 00:09:35,000
Changzhou!

184
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:37,039
Let's go!

185
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:00,600
Fall back! Fall back!

186
00:10:03,559 --> 00:10:04,519
Awesome!

187
00:10:05,759 --> 00:10:06,679
Awesome!

188
00:10:22,639 --> 00:10:23,279
Let's go!

189
00:10:23,639 --> 00:10:24,559
Let's go!

190
00:10:24,919 --> 00:10:25,759
Let's go!

191
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,080
Let's go!

192
00:10:27,519 --> 00:10:28,399
Let's go!

193
00:10:41,159 --> 00:10:42,759
Victory for Changzhou!

194
00:10:43,919 --> 00:10:45,519
Victory for Changzhou!

195
00:10:53,759 --> 00:10:55,639
Go Changzhou!

196
00:11:12,879 --> 00:11:13,679
It's a goal!

197
00:11:13,919 --> 00:11:15,279
Number 27, Zhou Hang!

198
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,639
What a beautiful curve!

199
00:11:16,759 --> 00:11:17,519
Top corner!

200
00:11:17,639 --> 00:11:18,960
Right in the top corner!

201
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:21,200
On his 27th birthday,

202
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:23,519
