203
00:11:23,639 --> 00:11:26,480
he opens up new possibilities for Changzhou FC.

204
00:11:26,799 --> 00:11:28,519
This ordinary company employee,

205
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,919
with exquisite footwork,

206
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,559
a sharp instinct near the goal,

207
00:11:31,679 --> 00:11:33,559
and tireless running,

208
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:34,919
shows us

209
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:37,559
what passion and perseverance truly mean.

210
00:11:44,360 --> 00:11:44,759
Come here.

211
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:46,799
Coach, you wanted me?

212
00:11:47,639 --> 00:11:48,840
Nice work out there today.

213
00:11:52,919 --> 00:11:53,639
Happy birthday.

214
00:11:55,799 --> 00:11:57,000
