233
00:12:46,279 --> 00:12:48,159
Parents always mean well.

234
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,000
What happened back then,

235
00:12:50,399 --> 00:12:51,360
just let it go.

236
00:12:52,279 --> 00:12:52,840
Besides,

237
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:53,879
it was their

238
00:12:53,879 --> 00:12:54,879
first time being parents too.

239
00:12:56,639 --> 00:12:57,440
Why do I feel like

240
00:12:57,799 --> 00:12:59,399
