246
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:10,720
The risks of going pro in soccer

247
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:11,840
aren't something every family

248
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:12,799
can afford to take on.

249
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:14,440
You have to understand them.

250
00:13:15,679 --> 00:13:17,559
I understood that long ago, Coach Chang.

251
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:19,879
Right now,

252
00:13:20,879 --> 00:13:21,519
I'm just happy.

253
00:13:22,559 --> 00:13:23,320
I'm happy that they

254
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,200
