262
00:14:04,879 --> 00:14:06,919
We're out of the quarterfinals anyway.

263
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:07,840
I made a wish

264
00:14:07,919 --> 00:14:08,799
to score one goal for myself.

265
00:14:10,919 --> 00:14:11,679
And I wish

266
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:13,679
every kid in the world who loves soccer

267
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,840
can play freely, without limits.
